\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Eating less food? Oh no. Mother had a good appetite.
