s found. He must have - carried the instrument upside down you see, and lost the mouthpiece. Remember having an hiding for that. But it was the only hiding I ever had I think. He was - he was - cut up over that. Because the mouthpiece - his favourite mout
hpiece. And sent out to the - oh it was found next morning.
