fternoon. Used to have - a - a - the Bible Catechi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14953012\charrsid10955930 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 
m and catechism for children. In Sunday school you know, yes, yes. Yes. Oh yes, had presents, always have a present, yes. Oh yes. We'd have some kind of present of course I mean nothing unusual. Things were different to then what they are now. Mm.
