\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Yes, oh yes, used to go, yes. Go in a brake then. In a brake. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 What about Bank Holidays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 I suppose there was, didn't make much difference to us, not at that - not at that age. Didn't have much of a bank holiday, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 I went to Swan - {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Swansea{\*\xmlclose} - my mother had - mother had a sister in 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Swansea{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
. And I used to go down there - on my hol - on the holiday on - on summer holiday. And they used to come up to our house you see, to share the - share the holiday as it were. Mm. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 For how long would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 For a fortnight - as a rule.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Would you go ever year, was it regular?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Yes, when I was a boy. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Only you went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Only myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Not the girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No. The girls - girls didn't go very far.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 What would you do when you went to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Swansea{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose} on holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Oh - go around the town with all - with my cousins. Yes, oh it was a wonderful - wonderful to go to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place
}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Swansea{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Could you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days, when you were a little boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 
Saturday? Now then - oh, we had to - clean the road - in front of the house. And - brush the road. And get enough sticks in for Sunday, enough coal in for Sunday. Enough water in for Sunday. Sunday was a very sacred day. And
 we had to - do all that kind of work, do everything else for Sunday. She wouldn't do any - if you could do it Saturday you shouldn't do it Sunday. And we used to prepare Saturday for Sunday. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 What about Sunday now? What did you do on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 
Go to service in morning. Sunday school. Sunday evening service, and - singing school or whatever would be in the nights afterwards. Sunday was a busy day. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did you have different clothes on Sunday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Oh yes, yes, yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did you play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No. Weren't allowed - weren't allowed to play games.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did your parents think it wrong to work or play on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No. No, Sunday was very - reserved. Should any - shouldn't do anything Sunday. We shouldn't - shouldn't do anythin
g Sunday, out of the way. Well you didn't have much time do you see. Didn't have much time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did your parents attend a place of worship or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Mm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did your parents attend a place of worship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Place of worship, did they go to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Yes, Groes, Beulah. Beulah Groes chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Welsh Presbyterian?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Welsh - Welsh - Methodist.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 How often would they go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Who now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Your father and mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Oh every Sunday. When she could go do you see. When the childr
en would allow her - when the children would be - old enough and so on. Oh yes, mother died faithful, and my father. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 How often would they go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Oh twice a Sunday. My mother'd be - home in the morning with the dinner of course. Then go to S
unday school. And - go the evening service.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did you go to Sunday school or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 You just said there was a Sunday school outing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 There was just the one in the year was there, one outing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Oh - well this Sunday school outing was one outing of course. That was the usual - Sunday school outing. And - go to 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Swansea{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} - go again, go to Aberavon. You - we didn't have to go far somehow. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Were there any other social activities organized by the chapel then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No, no, not - not - at - nothing outside that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 What did the choir do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Oh just take part in Sunday school. Sunday school used to have a choir, small choir. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Would there be any special performances or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Oh yes. Yes. Yes, when Maggie came - on the scene we had the other concerts and things see. Mm hm. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 That was when she was old enough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Yes, when she got old enough, yes. She used to have love - lovely concerts.
 When I was small used to have a - a - Sunday school, Sunday school was the main thing. Programme, and such things, see the programme. We could learn the programme - through out you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did the chapel run a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No. No, no temperance club, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did you belong to any other club organised by the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No, they had - they had - they didn't have anything else. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 On Sundays. Just on Sundays, yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Who would say it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Father. Uh huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Prayers at night, we used to say our own prayers of course, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No, not in the - no, not - not family prayers. Not family prayers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Do you know if your father took an interest in politics at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No. Not a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 You don't know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No, oh I wouldn't know, not, no, I couldn't say so. He was more concerned with music. Choir - and the band. Choir
 and the band, choir, he was bandsman. Belonged to the Secondary Welsh Regiment, and - the choirs in Taibach at the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 What about your mother, was she interested at all in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Do you ever remember them voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 I don't remember. I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 
In some places at that time men felt they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employers. Do you know if your father felt like that, under any kind of pressure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No, I don't think so. No, he - I don't think he was put under pressure at all. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Was he a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Party? Well at that time it - is Conservative and Liberal, at that time. That is Parliamentary -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Was your father ever interested in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No, not a lot I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did he ever work for one of the parties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 No. I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 What about your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Well I don't know, if - she didn't seem to bother much about it you see, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 
Well my mother of course had all sorts to do. Mending. With five children do you see. And my father were a miner - and - gardening of course, we had a large garden i
n Margam. And then he was out at band practice and choir practice. He was pretty busy in that respect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Oh chapel. Chapel, oh yes. Oh chapel once or twice a week - the evenings, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Neighbours. Neighbours. Yes. Some nice neighbours in Cwmbrombil then. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 When did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Oh at that time probably - half past five I should think, at that time, 'cos you worked longer hours then do you see.
