is the gardener and - his son, Alf Morris. And Edwin Morris I remember. They - they were two teachers you see, and then there was another teacher we had, Mr Sanderson. He was a teacher I remember now mostly. He was - of course I was only there you see fiv
e years you see. Oh Taibach school was a very good school, yes. Mm.
