Mm. I don't know. I don't know - I suppose teachers make a distinction more or less I suppose they do. But I - we didn't - and you were ignored.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 You didn't?
