No. Oh no. I didn't see no - your youth - and childhood then you can remember between. Now if you ask me between - I will be able to tell you. But - all these - the childhood - and - so on, I seem - to impress itself on you, doesn't it. Impress its
elf on you. You never forget your childhood. Tell you about my father with the choir etcetera. I can remember now - he had a model in this room - in the corner - only one room, the kitchen, you see, only the kitchen. We had two rooms then, the kitchen - a
nd bedroom, and a scullery - in - inside, that was built - when we went there I think. Well I can remember my father now - fixing up \{BLANK\} in the corner there, cupboard there, just like that now. And we used to get - be trained on }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14953012\charrsid10955930 sol-fa}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930  system.
