Very young. Yes. Oh yes, my father had lived - if my father had lived my life would have been far - far different to what it was, you know. Oh like like it effects every child doesn't it. Oh yes, oh - at that ag
e, ten - ten years of age you see. Mm. Yes, ten years of age, yes, mm. Yes.
