\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Well I don't know - about gangs. You'd choose - you - you'd choose a companion. Now my companion was - one of the 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Wellingtons{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 in Taibach. George - do you remember George Wellington? Well his brother David - well we - we - we got together somehow, and we used to play together. Funny thing that. Oh I suppose there were gangs, I suppose there were. But 
- you take take the Taibach now, the - the upper end, called the side you call it, no doubt there was gangs there do you see, or - in their way. In their way.
\par 
