\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Mm hm, in their way. They were more or less - I don't know - the - they
 were gang dwellers you see, they were more - rough than we were, we were brought up in the country do you see. Yes. No doubt about them.
