 on the estate. He used to employ a boy - when the servants would be old enough to come off - off nest as it were - used to - choose a wood under the covers for - and so many h
ens, and had so many chicks - for each hen do you see and - and I - and I happened to be - had a job for - for - for - the following year, so - I was very fortunate you know, I had to leave school then, probably I wouldn't have left otherwise. But I had t
his job came my way, and my mother was a widow of course.
