hap too, remember him? Oh he was marvellous. If you got stuck - if you got stuck - I remember doing stocks and shares if you please. To - to - drag up your arithmetic you see. A - funny thing, Willie Davis - Willie Davis - know Willie Davis Taibach? And N
a
tt Hayes, well we were in the same class, and they both became managers - of - of - what do you call it - exchange, after that. Well they were doing - civil works you see, engi - civil work. Civil - they were doing civil exams. And - if you got stuck he'd
 come over and look over you and said, what's the matter boy? He - in - in a couple of minutes have a page full of figures. Marvelous though.
