fection, or food or safety or discipline. What did you think was important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5452723 GM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 Well, it was coming natural when I was a parent. Yes. That's the function of a parents isn't it, yes. Mm.
