Clergy, yes, yes, clergy. Clergy. Well the clergy had their friends. There wouldn't - be many clergy coming here. We had a clergyman living next door. Clergy next door. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13836759 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13139658\charrsid10955930 What about the teachers?
